{"tid":1039877,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"DIY一個求生用的家用濾水器","createTime":"2019-02-27T16:57:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-27T21:23:25.000Z","uid":123956,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8323626ba98b9e61fe4cae0ca6918612ab10af67","tid":1039877,"uid":123956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T16:57:10.000Z","msg":"看到中国未來會支爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,加上看到太和村停水停電的苦況<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,所以想製造一個濾水器可快速又安全地循環生活污水(洗澡,洗碗,尿液) 和香港受污染的水(涉海/河水)。<br />\n目標是每日循環120公升的污水做食水。而每2次過濾才要做一次清洗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n參考網上傳統濾水器(炭加砂礫),可以有效分離出水出雜質,細菌病毒和寄生蟲可以用煲水的高溫殺死。<br />\n但 重金屬 和 化學污染 如何清除?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果用蒸餾法製出蒸餾水,經濟上無那麼多能源和錢去支持&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以請問濾水廠是如何清除食水中的 重金屬 和化學污染物?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />謝謝巴打和絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"021c0019af33f0f10af904381a3488e131bad850","tid":1039877,"uid":54574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T17:08:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.wsd.gov.hk/filemanager/tc/share/pdf/water_treat.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsd.gov.hk%2Ffilemanager%2Ftc%2Fshare%2Fpdf%2Fwater_treat.pdf&d=7eOXcRQmrlFTo7mkgo38hN%2FsvSzfkBtT%2Fd%2Bxj92WHuQ%3D&h=83c33880\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.wsd.gov.hk/filemanager/tc/share/pdf/water_treat.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"259fc469a00f7a20e934dc2d1122beec9718a1ee","tid":1039877,"uid":123956,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"021c0019af33f0f10af904381a3488e131bad850","tid":1039877,"uid":54574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T17:08:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.wsd.gov.hk/filemanager/tc/share/pdf/water_treat.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsd.gov.hk%2Ffilemanager%2Ftc%2Fshare%2Fpdf%2Fwater_treat.pdf&d=7eOXcRQmrlFTo7mkgo38hN%2FsvSzfkBtT%2Fd%2Bxj92WHuQ%3D&h=83c33880\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.wsd.gov.hk/filemanager/tc/share/pdf/water_treat.pdf</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T19:18:15.000Z","msg":"謝謝,但都是不足。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9cf4702283f69d70a5a91dc448fc7131fe0d2c5","tid":1039877,"uid":13491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T20:04:24.000Z","msg":"正皮，等睇完成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45b60b58c3b878cf1379e27693e2e0e38ce19bc7","tid":1039877,"uid":123956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9cf4702283f69d70a5a91dc448fc7131fe0d2c5","tid":1039877,"uid":13491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T20:04:24.000Z","msg":"正皮，等睇完成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T21:23:25.000Z","msg":"家中位置不多,如果以水務署計人均220公升/日,放2日便440公升,等於20支22公升的樽裝蒸餾水的空間,未計過濾器的體積和重量,未諗如何收集和處理污水時會遇到的麻煩問題。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除了收集時漏出會有衛生問題和臭味,最麻煩是每日每次都要做,(麻煩)是令人反對的最大原因。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最麻煩是家人的支持和配合,如果他們反對,最多只能找一個暗位放2-3支水便完了&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}